Tested with jboss-as-7.1.1.Final

1. Build project:
mvn clean install

2. Add user to JBoss7 server:
- run $JBOSS_HOME/bin/add-user.sh
- choose b) Application User (application-users.properties)
- choose ApplicationRealm
- Username : remoteuser
- Password: remote123$%
- do not add roles

3. Start server ($JBOSS_HOME/bin/standalone.bat)

4. Deploy to JBoss7 (JBoss should already be running):
cd ear
mvn jboss-as:deploy

5. Start client:
cd ejb-client
mvn exec:exec
